===message:I agree that what is pictured in Lange’s photo is hard for us to relate to because most Americans in our generation have always had food, clothing and shelter, plus most of our frivilous "wants". We are a very spoiled society of people, which is why many nations despise us. Also, it is true that the government was trying to “put a positive spin to a terrible time”.  That is so funny! Those pictures from the Visalia camp look so phony; the people are not even smiling while they are playing card games or while dancing.  And, like in our times, whatever spin the government puts out is what is recorded in the history books.
